title: xxxWILDEBEESTxxx
description:
SEE CONTENT LIST BELOW!!


Greetings from the North.

Welcome to WILDEBEEST, an Alternative Rock adventure from Denmark. 

The WILDEBEEST EP + THE LOOT will be distributed with a pro-sharing model, available for FREE download (mp3, wav) and spread over every network (website, social, youtube, spotify, torrent). 

WILDEBEEST works independently. NO Record label has been involved in this adventure and everything is self-produced and self-published. 

If you like what you hear, see or feel, please consider supporting WILDEBEEST:

# Buy the EP digipak. It will be signed and numbered. It will never be released again and is of very limited edition. 7.5 USD <a href="
http://mariamism.storenvy.com/products/457005-wildebeest-ep-limited-edition-signed-digipak" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://mariamism.storenvy.com/products/457005-wildebeest-ep-limited-edition-signed-digipak</a>

# Buy a download/donate via BandCamp to fund the creation of more music.  <a href="
http://wildebeestband.bandcamp.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://wildebeestband.bandcamp.com/</a>

# Share the music and videos with your friends or anyone else who might want to listen. Make this travel. Join the migration!

Any questions? Contact -W- via the form here: <a href="
http://wildebeestband.wordpress.com/connect/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://wildebeestband.wordpress.com/connect/</a>

The EP was published for looting on Jan 18 2013


THANK YOU FOR EVERYTHING YOU DO TO KEEP THIS GOING!


-W-
